jnxJsAntiVirus.description: This module defines the MIB for Juniper Enterprise specific antivirus functionality. Juniper documentation is recommended as the reference.

jnxJsAVEngineType.name: jnxJsAVEngineType
jnxJsAVEngineType.description: The scan engine type in use. User can use CLI to set the engine type to either full AV (kaspersky-lab-engine), express AV (juniper-express-engine) or Sophos AV (sophos-engine). If AV is not configured then engine type is not known.
